{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 1", "sort_key": "0001", "text_original": "天子玉藻，十有二旒，前後邃延，龍卷以祭。玄端而朝日於東門之外，聽朔於南門之外，閏月則闔門左扉，立於其中。皮弁以日視朝，遂以食，日中而餕，奏而食。日少牢，朔月大牢；五飲：上水、漿、酒、醴、酏。卒食，玄端而居。動則左史書之，言則右史書之，御瞽几聲之上下。年不順成，則天子素服，乘素車，食無樂。", "text_normalized": "天子玉藻，十有二旒，前後邃延，龍卷以祭。玄端而朝日於東門之外，聽朔於南門之外，閏月則闔門左扉，立於其中。皮弁以日視朝，遂以食，日中而餕，奏而食。日少牢，朔月大牢；五飲：上水、漿、酒、醴、酏。卒食，玄端而居。動則左史書之，言則右史書之，御瞽几聲之上下。年不順成，則天子素服，乘素車，食無樂。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 2", "sort_key": "0002", "text_original": "諸侯玄端以祭，裨冕以朝，皮弁以聽朔於大廟，朝服以日視朝於內朝。朝，辨色始入。君日出而視之，退適路寢，聽政，使人視大夫，大夫退，然後適小寢寢，釋服。又朝服以食，特牲三俎祭肺，夕深衣，祭牢肉，朔月少牢，五俎四簋，子卯稷食菜羹，夫人與君同庖。", "text_normalized": "諸侯玄端以祭，裨冕以朝，皮弁以聽朔於大廟，朝服以日視朝於內朝。朝，辨色始入。君日出而視之，退適路寢，聽政，使人視大夫，大夫退，然後適小寢寢，釋服。又朝服以食，特牲三俎祭肺，夕深衣，祭牢肉，朔月少牢，五俎四簋，子卯稷食菜羹，夫人與君同庖。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 3", "sort_key": "0003", "text_original": "君無故不殺牛，大夫無故不殺羊，士無故不殺犬、豕。君子遠庖廚，凡有血氣之類，弗身踐也。", "text_normalized": "君無故不殺牛，大夫無故不殺羊，士無故不殺犬、豕。君子遠庖廚，凡有血氣之類，弗身踐也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 4", "sort_key": "0004", "text_original": "至於八月不雨，君不舉。年不順成，君衣布搢本，關梁不租，山澤列而不賦，土功不興，大夫不得造車馬。", "text_normalized": "至於八月不雨，君不舉。年不順成，君衣布搢本，關梁不租，山澤列而不賦，土功不興，大夫不得造車馬。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 5", "sort_key": "0005", "text_original": "卜人定龜，史定墨，君定體。", "text_normalized": "卜人定龜，史定墨，君定體。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 6", "sort_key": "0006", "text_original": "君羔幦虎犆；大夫齊車，鹿幦豹犆，朝車；士齊車，鹿幦豹犆。", "text_normalized": "君羔幦虎犆；大夫齊車，鹿幦豹犆，朝車；士齊車，鹿幦豹犆。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 7", "sort_key": "0007", "text_original": "君子之居恒當戶，寢恒東首。若有疾風迅雷甚雨，則必變，雖夜必興，衣服冠而坐。日五盥，沐稷而靧粱，櫛用樿櫛，發曦用象櫛，進禨進羞，工乃升歌。浴用二巾，上絺下綌，出杅，履蒯席，連用湯，履蒲席，衣布曦身，乃屨進飲。將適公所，宿齊戒，居外寢，沐浴，史進象笏，書思對命；既服，習容觀玉聲，乃出，揖私朝，輝如也，登車則有光矣。", "text_normalized": "君子之居恒當戶，寢恒東首。若有疾風迅雷甚雨，則必變，雖夜必興，衣服冠而坐。日五盥，沐稷而靧粱，櫛用樿櫛，發曦用象櫛，進禨進羞，工乃升歌。浴用二巾，上絺下綌，出杅，履蒯席，連用湯，履蒲席，衣布曦身，乃屨進飲。將適公所，宿齊戒，居外寢，沐浴，史進象笏，書思對命；既服，習容觀玉聲，乃出，揖私朝，輝如也，登車則有光矣。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 8", "sort_key": "0008", "text_original": "天子搢挺，方正於天下也，諸侯荼，前詘後直，讓於天子也，大夫前詘後詘，無所不讓也。", "text_normalized": "天子搢挺，方正於天下也，諸侯荼，前詘後直，讓於天子也，大夫前詘後詘，無所不讓也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 9, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 9", "sort_key": "0009", "text_original": "侍坐，則必退席；不退，則必引而去君之黨。登席不由前，為躐席。徒坐不盡席尺，讀書，食，則齊，豆去席尺。", "text_normalized": "侍坐，則必退席；不退，則必引而去君之黨。登席不由前，為躐席。徒坐不盡席尺，讀書，食，則齊，豆去席尺。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 10, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 10", "sort_key": "0010", "text_original": "若賜之食而君客之，則命之祭，然後祭；先飯辯嘗羞，飲而俟。若有嘗羞者，則俟君之食，然後食，飯，飲而俟。", "text_normalized": "若賜之食而君客之，則命之祭，然後祭；先飯辯嘗羞，飲而俟。若有嘗羞者，則俟君之食，然後食，飯，飲而俟。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 11, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 11", "sort_key": "0011", "text_original": "君命之羞，羞近者，命之品嘗之，然後唯所欲。凡嘗遠食，必順近食。君未覆手，不敢飧；君既食，又飯飧，飯飧者，三飯也。君既徹，執飯與醬，乃出，授從者。", "text_normalized": "君命之羞，羞近者，命之品嘗之，然後唯所欲。凡嘗遠食，必順近食。君未覆手，不敢飧；君既食，又飯飧，飯飧者，三飯也。君既徹，執飯與醬，乃出，授從者。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 12, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 12", "sort_key": "0012", "text_original": "凡侑食，不盡食；食於人不飽。唯水漿不祭，若祭為已儕卑。", "text_normalized": "凡侑食，不盡食；食於人不飽。唯水漿不祭，若祭為已儕卑。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 13, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 13", "sort_key": "0013", "text_original": "君若賜之爵，則越席再拜稽首受，登席祭之，飲卒爵而俟君卒爵，然後授虛爵。君子之飲酒也，受一爵而色灑如也，二爵而言言斯，禮已三爵而油油以退，退則坐取屨，隱辟而後屨，坐左納右，坐右納左。", "text_normalized": "君若賜之爵，則越席再拜稽首受，登席祭之，飲卒爵而俟君卒爵，然後授虛爵。君子之飲酒也，受一爵而色灑如也，二爵而言言斯，禮已三爵而油油以退，退則坐取屨，隱辟而後屨，坐左納右，坐右納左。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 14, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 14", "sort_key": "0014", "text_original": "凡尊必上玄酒，唯君面尊，唯饗野人皆酒，大夫側尊用棜，士側尊用禁。", "text_normalized": "凡尊必上玄酒，唯君面尊，唯饗野人皆酒，大夫側尊用棜，士側尊用禁。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 15, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 15", "sort_key": "0015", "text_original": "始冠，緇布冠，自諸侯下達，冠而敝之可也。玄冠朱組纓，天子之冠也。緇布冠繢緌，諸侯之冠也。玄冠丹組纓，諸侯之齊冠也。玄冠綦組纓，士之齊冠也。縞冠玄武，子姓之冠也。縞冠素紕，既祥之冠也。垂緌五寸，惰游之士也，玄冠縞武，不齒之服也。居冠屬武，自天子下達，有事然後緌。五十不散送，親沒不髦，大帛不緌。衣冠紫緌，自魯桓公始也。", "text_normalized": "始冠，緇布冠，自諸侯下達，冠而敝之可也。玄冠朱組纓，天子之冠也。緇布冠繢緌，諸侯之冠也。玄冠丹組纓，諸侯之齊冠也。玄冠綦組纓，士之齊冠也。縞冠玄武，子姓之冠也。縞冠素紕，既祥之冠也。垂緌五寸，惰游之士也，玄冠縞武，不齒之服也。居冠屬武，自天子下達，有事然後緌。五十不散送，親沒不髦，大帛不緌。衣冠紫緌，自魯桓公始也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 16, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 16", "sort_key": "0016", "text_original": "朝玄端，夕深衣。深衣三袪，縫齊倍要，衽當旁，袂可以回肘。長中繼掩尺。袷二寸，祛尺二寸，緣廣寸半。以帛裹布，非禮也。", "text_normalized": "朝玄端，夕深衣。深衣三袪，縫齊倍要，衽當旁，袂可以回肘。長中繼掩尺。袷二寸，祛尺二寸，緣廣寸半。以帛裹布，非禮也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 17, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 17", "sort_key": "0017", "text_original": "士不衣織，無君者不貳采。衣正色，裳間色。", "text_normalized": "士不衣織，無君者不貳采。衣正色，裳間色。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 18, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 18", "sort_key": "0018", "text_original": "非列采不入公門，振絺綌不入公門，表裘不入公門，襲裘不入公門。", "text_normalized": "非列采不入公門，振絺綌不入公門，表裘不入公門，襲裘不入公門。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 19, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 19", "sort_key": "0019", "text_original": "纊為繭，縕為袍，禪為絅，帛為褶。", "text_normalized": "纊為繭，縕為袍，禪為絅，帛為褶。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 20, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 20", "sort_key": "0020", "text_original": "朝服之以縞也，自季康子始也。孔子曰：「朝服而朝，卒朔然後服之。」曰：「國家未道，則不充其服焉。」", "text_normalized": "朝服之以縞也，自季康子始也。孔子曰：「朝服而朝，卒朔然後服之。」曰：「國家未道，則不充其服焉。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 21, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 21", "sort_key": "0021", "text_original": "唯君有黼裘以誓省，大裘非古也。君衣狐白裘，錦衣以裼之。君之右虎裘，厥左狼裘。士不衣狐白。", "text_normalized": "唯君有黼裘以誓省，大裘非古也。君衣狐白裘，錦衣以裼之。君之右虎裘，厥左狼裘。士不衣狐白。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 22, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 22", "sort_key": "0022", "text_original": "君子狐青裘豹褎，玄綃衣以裼之；麑裘青豻褎，絞衣以裼之；羔裘豹飾，緇衣以裼之；狐裘，黃衣以裼之。錦衣狐裘，諸侯之服也。", "text_normalized": "君子狐青裘豹褎，玄綃衣以裼之；麑裘青豻褎，絞衣以裼之；羔裘豹飾，緇衣以裼之；狐裘，黃衣以裼之。錦衣狐裘，諸侯之服也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 23, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 23", "sort_key": "0023", "text_original": "犬羊之裘不裼，不文飾也不裼。裘之裼也，見美也。吊則襲，不盡飾也；君在則裼，盡飾也。服之襲也，充美也，是故尸襲，執玉龜襲，無事則裼，弗敢充也。", "text_normalized": "犬羊之裘不裼，不文飾也不裼。裘之裼也，見美也。吊則襲，不盡飾也；君在則裼，盡飾也。服之襲也，充美也，是故尸襲，執玉龜襲，無事則裼，弗敢充也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 24, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 24", "sort_key": "0024", "text_original": "笏：天子以球玉；諸侯以象；大夫以魚須文竹；士竹本，象可也。見於天子與射，無說笏，入大廟說笏，非古也。小功不說笏，當事免則說之。既搢必盥，雖有執於朝，弗有盥矣。凡有指畫於君前，用笏造，受命於君前，則書於笏，笏畢用也，因飾焉。笏度二尺有六寸，其中博三寸，其殺六分而去一。", "text_normalized": "笏：天子以球玉；諸侯以象；大夫以魚須文竹；士竹本，象可也。見於天子與射，無說笏，入大廟說笏，非古也。小功不說笏，當事免則說之。既搢必盥，雖有執於朝，弗有盥矣。凡有指畫於君前，用笏造，受命於君前，則書於笏，笏畢用也，因飾焉。笏度二尺有六寸，其中博三寸，其殺六分而去一。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 25, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 25", "sort_key": "0025", "text_original": "鞸，君朱，大夫素，士爵韋。圜殺直，天子直，公侯前後方，大夫前方後挫角，士前後正。", "text_normalized": "鞸，君朱，大夫素，士爵韋。圜殺直，天子直，公侯前後方，大夫前方後挫角，士前後正。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0026", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 26, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 26", "sort_key": "0026", "text_original": "鞸，下廣二尺，上廣一尺，長三尺，其頸五寸，肩革帶博二寸。", "text_normalized": "鞸，下廣二尺，上廣一尺，長三尺，其頸五寸，肩革帶博二寸。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0027", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 27, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 27", "sort_key": "0027", "text_original": "一命縕韍幽衡，再命赤韍幽衡，三命赤韍蔥衡。", "text_normalized": "一命縕韍幽衡，再命赤韍幽衡，三命赤韍蔥衡。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0028", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 28, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 28", "sort_key": "0028", "text_original": "天子素帶朱里終辟，而素帶終辟，大夫素帶辟垂，士練帶率下辟，居士錦帶，弟子縞帶。", "text_normalized": "天子素帶朱里終辟，而素帶終辟，大夫素帶辟垂，士練帶率下辟，居士錦帶，弟子縞帶。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0029", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 29, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 29", "sort_key": "0029", "text_original": "并紐約，用組、三寸，長齊於帶，紳長制，士三尺，有司二尺有五寸。子游曰：「參分帶下，紳居二焉，紳韍結三齊。」", "text_normalized": "并紐約，用組、三寸，長齊於帶，紳長制，士三尺，有司二尺有五寸。子游曰：「參分帶下，紳居二焉，紳韍結三齊。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0030", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 30, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 30", "sort_key": "0030", "text_original": "大夫大帶四寸。雜帶，君朱綠；大夫玄華，士緇辟，二寸，再繚四寸。凡帶，有率無箴功，肆束及帶勤者，有事則收之，走則擁之。", "text_normalized": "大夫大帶四寸。雜帶，君朱綠；大夫玄華，士緇辟，二寸，再繚四寸。凡帶，有率無箴功，肆束及帶勤者，有事則收之，走則擁之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0031", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 31, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 31", "sort_key": "0031", "text_original": "王后褘衣，夫人揄狄；君命屈狄，再命褘衣，一命襢衣，士褖衣。唯世婦命於奠繭，其他則皆從男子。", "text_normalized": "王后褘衣，夫人揄狄；君命屈狄，再命褘衣，一命襢衣，士褖衣。唯世婦命於奠繭，其他則皆從男子。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0032", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 32, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 32", "sort_key": "0032", "text_original": "凡侍於君，紳垂，足如履齊，頤溜垂拱，視下而聽上，視帶以及袷，聽鄉任左。", "text_normalized": "凡侍於君，紳垂，足如履齊，頤溜垂拱，視下而聽上，視帶以及袷，聽鄉任左。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0033", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 33, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 33", "sort_key": "0033", "text_original": "凡君召，以三節：二節以走，一節以趨。在官不俟屨，在外不俟車。", "text_normalized": "凡君召，以三節：二節以走，一節以趨。在官不俟屨，在外不俟車。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0034", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 34, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 34", "sort_key": "0034", "text_original": "士於大夫，不敢拜迎而拜送；士於尊者，先拜進面，答之拜則走。", "text_normalized": "士於大夫，不敢拜迎而拜送；士於尊者，先拜進面，答之拜則走。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0035", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 35, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 35", "sort_key": "0035", "text_original": "士於君所言，大夫沒矣，則稱謚若字，名士。與大夫言，名士字大夫。於大夫所，有公諱無私諱。凡祭不諱，廟中不諱，教學臨文不諱。", "text_normalized": "士於君所言，大夫沒矣，則稱謚若字，名士。與大夫言，名士字大夫。於大夫所，有公諱無私諱。凡祭不諱，廟中不諱，教學臨文不諱。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0036", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 36, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 36", "sort_key": "0036", "text_original": "古之君子必佩玉，右徵角，左宮羽。", "text_normalized": "古之君子必佩玉，右徵角，左宮羽。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0037", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 37, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 37", "sort_key": "0037", "text_original": "趨以《采齊》，行以《肆夏》，周還中規，折還中矩，進則揖之，退則揚之，然後玉鏘鳴也。故君子在車，則聞鸞和之聲，行則鳴佩玉，是以非辟之心，無自入也。", "text_normalized": "趨以《采齊》，行以《肆夏》，周還中規，折還中矩，進則揖之，退則揚之，然後玉鏘鳴也。故君子在車，則聞鸞和之聲，行則鳴佩玉，是以非辟之心，無自入也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0038", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 38, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 38", "sort_key": "0038", "text_original": "君在不佩玉，左結佩，右設佩，居則設佩，朝則結佩，齊則綪結佩而爵韍。", "text_normalized": "君在不佩玉，左結佩，右設佩，居則設佩，朝則結佩，齊則綪結佩而爵韍。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0039", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 39, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 39", "sort_key": "0039", "text_original": "凡帶必有佩玉，唯喪否。佩玉有沖牙；君子無故，玉不去身，君子於玉比德焉。天子佩白玉而玄組綬，公侯佩山玄玉而朱組綬，大夫佩水蒼玉而純組綬，世子佩瑜玉而綦組綬，士佩瓀玟而縕組綬。孔子佩象環五寸，而綦組綬。", "text_normalized": "凡帶必有佩玉，唯喪否。佩玉有沖牙；君子無故，玉不去身，君子於玉比德焉。天子佩白玉而玄組綬，公侯佩山玄玉而朱組綬，大夫佩水蒼玉而純組綬，世子佩瑜玉而綦組綬，士佩瓀玟而縕組綬。孔子佩象環五寸，而綦組綬。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0040", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 40, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 40", "sort_key": "0040", "text_original": "童子之節也，緇布衣錦緣，錦紳，并紐錦，束發皆朱錦也。童子不裘不帛，不屨絇，無緦服。聽事不麻，無事則立主人之北面，見先生從人而入。", "text_normalized": "童子之節也，緇布衣錦緣，錦紳，并紐錦，束發皆朱錦也。童子不裘不帛，不屨絇，無緦服。聽事不麻，無事則立主人之北面，見先生從人而入。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0041", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 41, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 41", "sort_key": "0041", "text_original": "侍食於先生異爵者，後祭先飯。客祭，主人辭曰：「不足祭也。」客飧，主人辭以疏。主人自置其醬，則客自徹之。一室之人，非賓客，一人徹。壹食之人，一人徹。凡燕食，婦人不徹。", "text_normalized": "侍食於先生異爵者，後祭先飯。客祭，主人辭曰：「不足祭也。」客飧，主人辭以疏。主人自置其醬，則客自徹之。一室之人，非賓客，一人徹。壹食之人，一人徹。凡燕食，婦人不徹。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0042", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 42, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 42", "sort_key": "0042", "text_original": "食棗桃李，弗致于核，瓜祭上環，食中棄所操。凡食果實者後君子，火孰者先君子。有慶，非君賜不賀。", "text_normalized": "食棗桃李，弗致于核，瓜祭上環，食中棄所操。凡食果實者後君子，火孰者先君子。有慶，非君賜不賀。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0043", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 43, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 43", "sort_key": "0043", "text_original": "孔子食於季氏，不辭，不食肉而飧。", "text_normalized": "孔子食於季氏，不辭，不食肉而飧。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0044", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 44, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 44", "sort_key": "0044", "text_original": "君賜車馬，乘以拜賜；衣服，服以拜賜；君未有命，弗敢即乘服也。君賜，稽首，據掌致諸地；酒肉之賜，弗再拜。凡賜，君子與小人不同日。", "text_normalized": "君賜車馬，乘以拜賜；衣服，服以拜賜；君未有命，弗敢即乘服也。君賜，稽首，據掌致諸地；酒肉之賜，弗再拜。凡賜，君子與小人不同日。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0045", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 45, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 45", "sort_key": "0045", "text_original": "凡獻於君，大夫使宰，士親，皆再拜稽首送之。膳於君，有葷桃茢，於大夫去茢，於士去葷，皆造於膳宰。大夫不親拜，為君之答己也。", "text_normalized": "凡獻於君，大夫使宰，士親，皆再拜稽首送之。膳於君，有葷桃茢，於大夫去茢，於士去葷，皆造於膳宰。大夫不親拜，為君之答己也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0046", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 46, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 46", "sort_key": "0046", "text_original": "大夫拜賜而退，士待諾而退，又拜，弗答拜。大夫親賜士，士拜受，又拜於其室。衣服，弗服以拜。敵者不在，拜於其室。", "text_normalized": "大夫拜賜而退，士待諾而退，又拜，弗答拜。大夫親賜士，士拜受，又拜於其室。衣服，弗服以拜。敵者不在，拜於其室。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0047", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 47, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 47", "sort_key": "0047", "text_original": "凡於尊者有獻，而弗敢以聞。士於大夫不承賀，下大夫於上大夫承賀。親在，行禮於人稱父，人或賜之，則稱父拜之。", "text_normalized": "凡於尊者有獻，而弗敢以聞。士於大夫不承賀，下大夫於上大夫承賀。親在，行禮於人稱父，人或賜之，則稱父拜之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0048", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 48, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 48", "sort_key": "0048", "text_original": "禮不盛，服不充，故大裘不裼，乘路車不式。", "text_normalized": "禮不盛，服不充，故大裘不裼，乘路車不式。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0049", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 49, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 49", "sort_key": "0049", "text_original": "父命呼，唯而不諾，手執業則投之，食在口則吐之，走而不趨。親老，出不易方，復不過時。親癠色容不盛，此孝子之疏節也。", "text_normalized": "父命呼，唯而不諾，手執業則投之，食在口則吐之，走而不趨。親老，出不易方，復不過時。親癠色容不盛，此孝子之疏節也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0050", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 50, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 50", "sort_key": "0050", "text_original": "父歿而不能讀父之書，手澤存焉爾；母歿而杯圈不能飲焉，口澤之氣存焉爾。", "text_normalized": "父歿而不能讀父之書，手澤存焉爾；母歿而杯圈不能飲焉，口澤之氣存焉爾。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0051", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 51, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 51", "sort_key": "0051", "text_original": "君入門，介拂闑，大夫中棖與闑之間，士介拂棖。賓入不中門，不履閾，公事自闑西，私事自闑東。", "text_normalized": "君入門，介拂闑，大夫中棖與闑之間，士介拂棖。賓入不中門，不履閾，公事自闑西，私事自闑東。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0052", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 52, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 52", "sort_key": "0052", "text_original": "君與尸行接武，大夫繼武，士中武，徐趨皆用是。疾趨則欲發而手足毋移，圈豚行不舉足，齊如流，席上亦然。端行，頤溜如矢，弁行，剡剡起屨，執龜玉，舉前曳踵，蹜蹜如也。", "text_normalized": "君與尸行接武，大夫繼武，士中武，徐趨皆用是。疾趨則欲發而手足毋移，圈豚行不舉足，齊如流，席上亦然。端行，頤溜如矢，弁行，剡剡起屨，執龜玉，舉前曳踵，蹜蹜如也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0053", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 53, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 53", "sort_key": "0053", "text_original": "凡行容愓愓，廟中齊齊，朝庭濟濟翔翔。君子之容舒遲，見所尊者齊遫。足容重，手容恭，目容端，口容止，聲容靜，頭容直，氣容肅，立容德，色容莊，坐如尸，燕居告溫溫。", "text_normalized": "凡行容愓愓，廟中齊齊，朝庭濟濟翔翔。君子之容舒遲，見所尊者齊遫。足容重，手容恭，目容端，口容止，聲容靜，頭容直，氣容肅，立容德，色容莊，坐如尸，燕居告溫溫。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0054", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 54, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 54", "sort_key": "0054", "text_original": "凡祭，容貌顏色，如見所祭者。喪容纍纍，色容顛顛，視容瞿瞿梅梅，言容繭繭，戎容暨暨，言容詻詻，色容厲肅，視容清明。立容辨，卑毋諂，頭頸必中，山立時行，盛氣顛實，揚休玉色。", "text_normalized": "凡祭，容貌顏色，如見所祭者。喪容纍纍，色容顛顛，視容瞿瞿梅梅，言容繭繭，戎容暨暨，言容詻詻，色容厲肅，視容清明。立容辨，卑毋諂，頭頸必中，山立時行，盛氣顛實，揚休玉色。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0055", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap", "source_id": "liji-013-the-jade-bead-pendants-of-the-royal-cap__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 55, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《玉藻》 55", "sort_key": "0055", "text_original": "凡自稱：天子曰予一人，伯曰天子之力臣。諸侯之於天子曰某土之守臣某，其在邊邑，曰某屏之臣某。其於敵以下曰寡人，小國之君曰孤，擯者亦曰孤。上大夫曰下臣，擯者曰寡君之老，下大夫自名，擯者曰寡大夫。世子自名，擯者曰寡君之適，公子曰臣孽。士曰傳遽之臣，於大夫曰外私。大夫私事使，私人擯則稱名，公士擯則曰寡大夫、寡君之老。大夫有所往，必與公士為賓也。", "text_normalized": "凡自稱：天子曰予一人，伯曰天子之力臣。諸侯之於天子曰某土之守臣某，其在邊邑，曰某屏之臣某。其於敵以下曰寡人，小國之君曰孤，擯者亦曰孤。上大夫曰下臣，擯者曰寡君之老，下大夫自名，擯者曰寡大夫。世子自名，擯者曰寡君之適，公子曰臣孽。士曰傳遽之臣，於大夫曰外私。大夫私事使，私人擯則稱名，公士擯則曰寡大夫、寡君之老。大夫有所往，必與公士為賓也。", "notes": ""}
